    """Equation to be evolved.

    Background:
    Calculate Acceleration in Nonl-linear Harmonic Oscillator given Position at time t and Velocity at time t

    Variables:
    - Independents: x0, x1
- Dependent: y

    Parameters:
    - params (np.ndarray): Trainable coefficients used by the equation skeleton.
    """
    """Improved version of `equation_v1`.

    This version refines the nonlinear harmonic oscillator acceleration model by including
    physically interpretable polynomial terms up to cubic order in position (x0) and velocity (x1),
