        params[4]: quadratic position term coefficient
        params[5]: quadratic velocity term coefficient
        params[6]: cross term coefficient (x0 * x1)
        params[7]: cubic velocity term coefficient (x1^3)
        params[8]: mixed cubic term coefficient ((x0^2)*x1)
        params[9]: mixed cubic term coefficient (x0*(x1^2))
        params[10]: quartic position term coefficient (x0^4)
        params[11]: quartic velocity term coefficient (x1^4)

    Returns:
    - y (np.ndarray): acceleration values.
