        - c * x1                  # linear damping (-c*v)
        + p[3] * x0 ** 2          # quadratic stiffness term
        + p[4] * x1 ** 2          # quadratic damping term
        + p[5] * x0 ** 3          # cubic stiffness term (Duffing nonlinearity)
        + p[6] * x0 * x1          # cross coupling linear*linear
        + p[7] * x0 ** 2 * x1     # cross coupling quadratic*linear velocity
        + p[8] * x0 * x1 ** 2     # cross coupling linear*quadratic velocity
        + p[9] * x0 ** 3 * x1     # higher order cross coupling
        + p[10] * x0 * x1 ** 3     # higher order cross coupling
        + p[11] * x1 ** 3         # cubic damping term
    )
    
    return y
